o para TVP PROXIMAL principalmente","guid":"03yCmrDXTUiQb2ViWtAm1w","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"114","text":"PMID: 16027455","guid":"eeouhR1WTLKVi9Kd2GiTHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"102","text":"DÍMERO D","guid":"ujF1ShhoRsGG5GgYlWbEZQ","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"ELISA cuantitativo de alta sensibilidad","guid":"_5y36cyBTD6FyYxr8l0cng","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Corte estándar <500 ng/mL → VPN >97% si pretest baja-intermedia","guid":"GVQcArXOSsKYG1vxzr43kw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"LR- ~0.10 (descarta en pretest baja)","guid":"yy8xDA25T2yEfGUmbBscWA","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"120","text":"LR+ pobre (~1.5) → NO sirve para confirmar","guid":"onmeKAMkRm-IcgqJ1LfL7g","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"120","text":"AJUSTE POR EDAD (>50a) → corte = edad x 10 ng/mL","guid":"z_W0a1r5Taa_SddfihdSng","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Ej: 80 años → corte 800 ng/mL","guid":"Q1lidevZRJ-nJz6jzalbmQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"ADJUST-PE → ↑ exclusiones 6→30% en >75a sin falsos negativos","guid":"u6q_JejzRCWrqYGmaLfhuQ","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"PMID: 24643601","guid":"-9nDb2InT5GrNnEmETpA-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"120","text":"LIMITACIONES EN AM","guid":"2gI1tVdgScSdr0RyhydorQ","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"Dímero D fisiológicamente ↑ con edad","guid":"feyEzY98TqmbtOjsps9vLQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"Comorbilidades elevan basal (cáncer, infección, IC)","guid":"hzhEJhqBSDSjOu0t4Y534w","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"Especificidad cae con edad","guid":"WILjkAtVRPKZ1Us1glKlHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"120","text":"NO solicitar trombofilia en agudo (alteraciones por trombo activo)","guid":"d2dNW-SsQBC14DWv4E1JAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"102","text":"ECO DOPPLER VENOSO COMPRESIÓN","guid":"_6AAMTR0ShSJ6RlzL0uO1g","children"