OLOGÍA (ASH 2020 Rec 12-14)","guid":"eOeavqzHSQ2T6m4_-Npldw","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"PROVOCADA factor TRANSITORIO → 3-6 meses, suspender","guid":"yRKpOyxeT3yPMoleOOoIGg","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"PROVOCADA factor CRÓNICO → indefinida (Rec 18, condicional)","guid":"hOCfA0v3Qemu-N0rgtmv2A","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"214","text":"NO PROVOCADA → indefinida tras tto primario (Rec 19, condicional)","guid":"CWFX8yYfQSS1R6BZFkw9Ow","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"214","text":"RECURRENTE no provocada → indefinida (Rec 25, FUERTE)","guid":"vk2yZOCAQZ-W1XyYePr2zQ","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"214","text":"TVP asociada a CÁNCER → indefinida mientras cáncer activo","guid":"WocAL4xJTyS-rrlfytCMDA","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"212","text":"FASE EXTENDIDA → DOSIS REDUCIDA (ASH 2020 Rec 22)","guid":"9VY2H-L1T6OaKoYMD11aYQ","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"APIXABAN 2.5mg c/12h","guid":"-ZZFCqWVSGyripOYkz_6fQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"RIVAROXABAN 10mg/día","guid":"rctmIMqBQGSopkTx3YRtAg","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"220","text":"Mantener eficacia con menor sangrado vs dosis estándar","guid":"r9wdrZVsQyyQJj_PTv98-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"224","parent":"212","text":"SCORES RIESGO RECURRENCIA (uso NO rutinario, Rec 15)","guid":"LtpqfHSpQXyPcSJCJqWt7w","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"HERDOO2 (mujeres)","guid":"0RWiHozrRXSzkWz8OXftUA","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"224","text":"Vienna prediction model","guid":"j9_jAJrVT0GrlpiHE7CP-Q","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"224","text":"DASH score","guid":"l6ELj77ZTLmz8yIoO8cE5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"228","parent":"212","text":"SCORES RIESGO SANGRADO","guid":"d0TCGcnZSOW6JuFFkgXWGw","children":[{"id":"229","parent":"228","text":"HAS-BLED → desarrollado para FA, NO validado en VTE","guid":"hDfr6KPqQLWdUjA9g4PYFA","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"228","text":"VTE-BLEED, RIETE → más específicos","guid":"Wu6VpOwLTCSWAswuI2iOsg","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"212","text":"REEVALUACIÓN ANUAL en AM → balance riesgo/beneficio dinámico","guid":"QIreevmpTPu_d932Q2axJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIÁTRICAS CRÍTICAS","guid":"bQe1tbAeRveQ73KY03cd2g","children":[{"id":"233","parent":"232","text":"FUNCIÓN RENAL → DETERMINANTE de selección","guid":"31QcnystSgKKbuphQoTm0A","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"APIXABAN → más permisivo, Crcl ≥15 (preferido en AM)","guid":"bQzga3cpQ4y8nzpYG-BVfw","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"RIVAROXABAN → Crcl ≥15 con cautela","guid":"Ji46mx4XRquthWJqPV2a0w","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"EDOXABAN → evitar Crcl <30 o >95","guid":"H9ZHXTmGTJuI3oS_L6eT0Q","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"233","text":"DABIGATRAN → evitar Crcl <30","guid":"QvLkKIT9Sm-R84Dv0ldzwA","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"233","text":"HBPM → ajustar 1mg/kg/día si Crcl <30","guid":"sBI91SEkQ5WTmy7R7huglQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"232","text":"POLIFARMACIA E INTERACCIONES","guid":"dsiTqevvSWam0ZI4JEMOBw","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"Inhibidores potentes CYP3A4 + P-gp → ↑ DOACs","guid":"Iq-ICZW3Tpe7Xbl6SEf8Uw","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"Azoles (ketoconazol, itraconazol)","guid":"IvtClMqrRg6_SuZpMfIy8A","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"240","text":"Claritromicina, eritromicina","guid":"Jdb4jNnVR2C3jw8fY4NjLQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"240","text":"Inhibidores proteasa","guid":"dbJXiFjiQD-iZkZcpIMymg","children":[]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"239","text":"Inductores → ↓ DOACs","guid":"pjn1BGhUS3eYUrO-nHf2_Q","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"Fenitoína, carbamazepina, fenobarbital","guid":"UnfIxCEMSKe9Y-f1-jj7Ig","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"Rifampicina","guid":"HGsoT_gZTgOqx52TbnNE_w","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"244","text":"Hierba de San Juan","guid":"C4V4KG9WTiyJCc7s8BMvdQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"248","parent":"239","text":"AINEs + anticoagulación → ↑ sangrado GI (especialmente ibuprofeno)","guid":"jsu3iYXqRgaZqdDT4h12nQ","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"239","text":"ISRS + anticoagulación → ↑ sangrado","guid":"4c_SrZasR_-ReWfiIFE2bw","children":[]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"232","text":"FRAGILIDAD Y CAÍDAS","guid":"q589baAQT_-OsTGRUNuwFw","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"CFS alto NO contraindica anticoagulación per se","guid":"aX8DBR56TsifE09jaePgnw","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"250","text":"Riesgo absoluto sangrado por caída es BAJO vs riesgo recurrencia","guid":"FhrwZRkASTGbwQo4oL6kmg","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"250","text":"NNH para hematoma subdural por caída en anticoagulado >295 caídas/año (Man-Son-Hing 1999)","guid":"EMgu7T_NQSGX7V8UjKH11w","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"250","text":"NO usar caídas como excusa para no anticoagular AM con VTE confirmada","guid":"ffe0KFITS-a-pu6yS6A6ig","children":[]}]},{"id":"255","parent":"232","text":"BALANCE RIESGO/BENEFICIO","guid":"eC_fZnRGTLS5dUHu7G5Q_w","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"VTE recurrente puede ser MORTAL","guid":"ApzB4KOeQQ69mNciTfYvNQ","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"255","text":"Sangrado mayor anticoagulación 2-3% año","guid":"_AUJYUnXReG4O85AaBqDPQ","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"255","text":"APIXABAN preferido por menor sangrado mayor (AMPLIFY → 0.6% vs 1.8% conv, RR 0.31)","guid":"zWQ7vr_5QLuiMkXukJkiNA","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"255","text":"Comunicación con paciente y familia → decisión compartida","guid":"35Hvomb2QRmkW8kU5dPQsw","children":[]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"232","text":"REVERSIÓN DE ANTICOAGULACIÓN","guid":"hVr8BRuZRdKPYVy0I6muHw","children":[{"id":"261","parent":"260","text":"DABIGATRAN → IDARUCIZUMAB 5g EV","guid":"ucWijVRsQqeH31PQzpiyIA","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"260","text":"APIXABAN/RIVAROXABAN → ANDEXANET ALFA (alto costo, limitada disponibilidad)","guid":"NnQ2zosORnyKJQ4FJN0Yyw","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"260","text":"Alternativa → CCP 4 factores 50 U/kg","guid":"CaPYJyzeRz-SVZklBB6Y2g","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"260","text":"WARFARINA → CCP 4 factores + vitamina K 10mg EV","guid":"trQCtRz-THyeJKjWYt1zpg","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"260","text":"HNF → PROTAMINA 1mg por 100U HNF (máx 50mg)","guid":"EmWGTL3WRtazn3tBvuli4Q","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"260","text":"HBPM → PROTAMINA reversión parcial (~60%)","guid":"_kZDNSJJQtairNKKHgPlCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"232","text":"SUSPENSIÓN PERIPROCEDIMIENTO","guid":"ymNdVf5oSZSk1JQx4n7TkA","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"DOAC → 24-48h previo a procedimiento bajo riesgo","guid":"e79DFtoYSeuKsX9buHrPTw","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"267","text":"DOAC → 48-72h previo a procedimiento alto riesgo (más si IR)","guid":"_sStn5TbSASfvHkR4LDSsQ","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"267","text":"Reanudar 24h post procedimiento si hemostasia adecuada","guid":"ZkTTH0xPTUK9ExTpFBqrOw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"271","parent":"0","text":"SITUACIONES ESPECIALES","guid":"gKrX9_zbSF2YAKSM0N7Fbg","children":[{"id":"272","parent":"271","text":"TVP EN CÁNCER","guid":"w4cFhvcOS5OQ6LZ999Q_XQ","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"HBPM clásicamente → ahora DOACs no inferiores en mayoría","guid":"4ovm73cuQ7WozfGHExrZmQ","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"272","text":"Apixaban y edoxaban con buena evidencia (ADAM VTE, Caravaggio)","guid":"At3HSsDcSeS3bXzzOlwe8Q","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"272","text":"Cáncer GI luminal (gástrico, colon) → cuidado sangrado con DOACs","guid":"GSwtBiaXRQiZSj5m3uz2hg","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"272","text":"Tumores cerebrales → individualizar","guid":"AXX8xw1rSt2oWvIe4C84Ew","children":[]}]},{"id":"277","parent":"271","text":"TVP EN EMBARAZO","guid":"nid1UOmGSCyA1pIkTxfYJw","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"HBPM → fármaco de elección","guid":"0G-wHYMAQn2HfyCFz0sYtg","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"277","text":"EVITAR warfarina (teratogénica) y DOACs (excretados leche, no datos)","guid":"jDPADXj0RpClUsv8EsOXow","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"277","text":"Continuar 6 semanas postparto, total mínimo 3 meses","guid":"MSLxHx8FSwCv6RtXyb_naA","children":[]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"271","text":"TROMBOCITOPENIA INDUCIDA POR HEPARINA (HIT)","guid":"KJQUKhsuTSuwJyaj2EJ0DQ","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"Sospecha → plaquetas <50% basal entre día 5-10 heparina","guid":"0M5LPGIYSDacz4LzB8Cdow","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"281","text":"SUSPENDER HEPARINA inmediatamente","guid":"l0IYkPcmTqmIcrfaAWg-vA","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"281","text":"Iniciar inhibidor directo trombina (argatroban, bivalirudina)","guid":"OIZ5Xc-8R3u9hFVA10GBXw","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"281","text":"NO transfundir plaquetas","guid":"ygcgaT2QSW6x6NiQ1tN1jw","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"281","text":"Score 4T para estratificación","guid":"jX_d1oaVSNu29JBctNaujg","children":[]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"271","text":"TVP MMSS","guid":"cUvuAJccRce63ibcHyxuTA","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"Anticoagulación 3 meses si provocada por catéter","guid":"uxvwo7EFQBS-RPLTmXeRYA","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"Retirar catéter SOLO si necesario, no urgente","guid":"zmvYmYGeTtqRfommmvVTnQ","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"287","text":"Trombolisis NO rutinaria","guid":"ovnxkToYTEa19fqUT0hncg","children":[]}]},{"id":"291","parent":"271","text":"SÍNDROME DE MAY-THURNER","guid":"HnZeHWVZQBWZFL2i1FHI6w","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"Compresión vena ilíaca izq por arteria ilíaca der","guid":"930iD0WUS96SPBXgRdbYpQ","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"291","text":"Considerar en TVP iliofemoral izquierda recurrente","guid":"QDKd4YW7Q2Gw6utPMFiMmA","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"291","text":"Tratamiento endovascular (stent) si sintomático","guid":"W2O4IV0TRLSWBUjBJjvLuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"295","parent":"271","text":"VTE INCIDENTAL en imagen","guid":"a9NWsJ1aS_qi7Xj_snxuvw","children":[{"id":"296","parent":"295","text":"Tratar igual que sintomática","guid":"vaR1orxTTxucHduX_s6ing","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"297","parent":"0","text":"COMPLICACIONES","guid":"xDv38UilRMmU-k_2-xUX9g","children":[{"id":"298","parent":"297","text":"EMBOLIA PULMONAR","guid":"PqvfkukZQd2J23_DDQM0Uw","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"Continuum del VTE → causa principal mortalidad TVP","guid":"k3vc_CWHQieZzDyo2nlRlw","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"298","text":"Sospecha clínica → ver mapa MUE_TEP","guid":"zySLLmnAR92W2tv4iXY-Xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"301","parent":"297","text":"SÍNDROME POSTROMBÓTICO (SPT)","guid":"QbONHiLgS8yAOmBbWetfJg","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"20-50% post TVP proximal","guid":"EVh3cXIJSYSshFVY01sAPg","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"301","text":"Dolor crónico, edema, hiperpigmentación, úlceras venosas","guid":"qrNZyh9FRtiV7L0pnz5WGg","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"301","text":"Mayor riesgo en TVP iliofemoral","guid":"Ry8QagJzQyimkvVg3ViTAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"305","parent":"297","text":"HIPERTENSIÓN PULMONAR TROMBOEMBÓLICA CRÓNICA","guid":"3F-qvrujSVq1lQdZMeVpDA","children":[{"id":"306","parent":"305","text":"Hasta 5% post TEP no resuelto","guid":"6tbxL1pjQZ2Uh5qDn79deQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"307","parent":"297","text":"RECURRENCIA","guid":"v8OSQD3uRE-ra5v0Zohh2w","children":[{"id":"308","parent":"307","text":"25-30% a 5 años en no provocada","guid":"vergCmizT62XpQa7sTUI5g","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"307","text":"6-9% año 1 sin anticoagulación","guid":"oYj9mkUtTNqCj-om8MsVJw","children":[]}]},{"id":"310","parent":"297","text":"SANGRADO POR ANTICOAGULACIÓN","guid":"KgoFvCUBRXaPbG8U5BVWaw","children":[{"id":"311","parent":"310","text":"Mayor 2-3% año","guid":"5QZF3iwPRBOBYkBuAgLAYQ","children":[]},{"id":"312","parent":"310","text":"Fatal 0.2-0.5% año","guid":"Q2g81fBZQ-meso-zb2DdKQ","children":[]},{"id":"313","parent":"310","text":"GI más frecuente con rivaroxaban y dabigatran","guid":"xMBopuG1Seq_r3BHCrkTHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"314","parent":"297","text":"HIT, OSTEOPOROSIS por heparinas, alopecia warfarina","guid":"y6MBEVCHRzisPG5ybvH6dQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"315","parent":"0","text":"PERLAS CLÍNICAS","guid":"xEHsr-xoQQuWdyDDwZYXBg","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR → SOSPECHAR TVP frente a deterioro funcional agudo, edema asimétrico nuevo, o delirium sin foco claro","guid":"P3o8vpMSTbmyq-Zi1uPKKQ","children":[]},{"id":"317","parent":"315","text":"Edema bilateral en AM con IC NO descarta TVP → asimetría >3cm es bandera roja","guid":"_fTRQZi9RIqMtHFJtaaUoQ","children":[]},{"id":"318","parent":"315","text":"Dímero D NEGATIVO + Wells improbable → DESCARTA TVP (eventos a 3 meses 0.4%)","guid":"Ryqa29lUQ3SKjJuIXSTiNQ","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"315","text":"Usar AJUSTE POR EDAD en >50 años → casi 5x más exclusiones en >75a sin perder seguridad","guid":"WGD0aSKIRrKa2kRjLQ6kyw","children":[]},{"id":"320","parent":"315","text":"HALLAZGOS clínicos individuales (Homans, calor, dolor) NO sirven aislados → SIEMPRE Wells o equivalente","guid":"zAegbATiRTOom_uZHNs7DQ","children":[]},{"id":"321","parent":"315","text":"APIXABAN preferido en AM frágil → menor sangrado mayor vs warfarina (NNT bleeding ~83 a 6 meses, AMPLIFY)","guid":"0djstJGkScSE5QhZsyZ03Q","children":[]},{"id":"322","parent":"315","text":"DOAC de inicio sin lead-in (apixaban, rivaroxaban) → simplifica manejo en AM","guid":"ElX_-7LhQn-RqV1jyIhGEQ","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"315","text":"Crcl <30 → APIXABAN sigue siendo opción (más permisivo); evitar dabigatran/edoxaban","guid":"KmqWgeDJQmSPGtfbwhPxdg","children":[]},{"id":"324","parent":"315","text":"Caídas NO contraindican anticoagulación → riesgo VTE recurrente >>> riesgo sangrado por caída","guid":"Jf4k1JxmTru2jgkr9AQU5Q","children":[]},{"id":"325","parent":"315","text":"Fractura cadera + TVP → evento centinela, anticoagulación + ortogeriatría coordinada","guid":"SKYppQf7SJWPFL9282-BtA","children":[]},{"id":"326","parent":"315","text":"PHLEGMASIA CERULEA DOLENS → emergencia, trombolisis dirigida por catéter","guid":"lgRHvWTkSsmERQtHgbpahw","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"315","text":"Filtro VCI → restrictivo en AM, retirar ASAP cuando recuperable","guid":"ksthR46yRF6KMLxmYysFaw","children":[]},{"id":"328","parent":"315","text":"Trombofilia NO solicitar en agudo → falsos positivos por trombo activo y heparina","guid":"fGOogZrlTgWDYZte_OJrVg","children":[]},{"id":"329","parent":"315","text":"Movilización precoz NO aumenta TEP → no reposo prolongado innecesario","guid":"0sy1T_kqSPai3AkKmezD_Q","children":[]},{"id":"330","parent":"315","text":"Compresión elástica → NO uso rutinario para prevenir SPT (ASH 2020) pero útil sintomáticamente","guid":"0Bx5b3nrSu6iIxVu9-zbqg","children":[]},{"id":"331","parent":"315","text":"TVP en cáncer → DOACs aceptados excepto GI luminal alto riesgo sangrado","guid":"IZeHgPGGSAaOJRu3GxPfmA","children":[]},{"id":"332","parent":"315","text":"Reanudar DOAC 24h post procedimiento bajo riesgo si hemostasia OK","guid":"NdYU-3jpRmq1635jKPZE0g","children":[]},{"id":"333","parent":"315","text":"Referencias","guid":"l3hjg1cySq-IunS7OKONsg","children":[{"id":"334","parent":"333","text":"1. Ortel TL, et al. American Society of Hematology 2020 guidelines for management of venous thromboembolism: treatment of deep vein thrombosis and pulmonary embolism. Blood Adv. 2020;4(19):4693-4738. PMID: 33007077","guid":"nHlOligSRVi5EK2QY5lJMg","children":[]},{"id":"335","parent":"333","text":"2. Stevens SM, et al. Antithrombotic Therapy for VTE Disease: Second Update of the CHEST Guideline. Chest. 2021;160(6):2247-2259. PMID: 34352279","guid":"_k0IfyvpRgSMMd0m6Nan2g","children":[]},{"id":"336","parent":"333","text":"3. Konstantinides SV, et al. 2019 ESC Guidelines for the diagnosis and management of acute pulmonary embolism developed in collaboration with the ERS. Eur Heart J. 2020;41(4):543-603.","guid":"Da7sUFXaRrmyzA-ljL7_Qg","children":[]},{"id":"337","parent":"333","text":"4. Goodacre S, Sutton AJ, Sampson FC. Meta-analysis: The value of clinical assessment in the diagnosis of deep venous thrombosis. Ann Intern Med. 2005;143(2):129-39. PMID: 16027455","guid":"uiVX35HPSP6ME6WRkkCstA","children":[]},{"id":"338","parent":"333","text":"5. Wells PS, et al. Evaluation of D-dimer in the diagnosis of suspected deep-vein thrombosis. N Engl J Med. 2003;349(13):1227-35. PMID: 14507948","guid":"ZwJ4AWsGRa6C4c8gdWiJGQ","children":[]},{"id":"339","parent":"333","text":"6. Righini M, et al. Age-adjusted D-dimer cutoff levels to rule out pulmonary embolism: the ADJUST-PE study. JAMA. 2014;311(11):1117-24. PMID: 24643601","guid":"WznIT5LQR4Kr0L3vB95xhg","children":[]},{"id":"340","parent":"333","text":"7. Agnelli G, et al. Oral apixaban for the treatment of acute venous thromboembolism (AMPLIFY). N Engl J Med. 2013;369(9):799-808. PMID: 23808982","guid":"c7iYDwDYQzidh29DvBFS4A","children":[]},{"id":"341","parent":"333","text":"8. Bauersachs R, et al. EINSTEIN Investigators. Oral rivaroxaban for symptomatic venous thromboembolism. N Engl J Med. 2010;363(26):2499-2510. PMID: 23846019","guid":"ryuVscT6Tx6NODRBtqyOKQ","children":[]},{"id":"342","parent":"333","text":"9. Buller HR, et al. Hokusai-VTE Investigators. Edoxaban versus warfarin for the treatment of symptomatic venous thromboembolism. N Engl J Med. 2013;369(15):1406-15. PMID: 23991658","guid":"q22dF_MLRhWrh_SJyNSpGw","children":[]},{"id":"343","parent":"333","text":"10. Schulman S, et al. RE-COVER Study Group. Dabigatran versus warfarin in the treatment of acute venous thromboembolism. N Engl J Med. 2009;361(24):2342-52. PMID: 19966341","guid":"GRweiAJWS_6UH07VvQ-K_g","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":343,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Medicina de Urgencia","folder":"MUE - Medicina de Urgencia","filename":"MUE_TVP","id":"map_2516","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"MUE_TVP"}